text: Reasonable price, fresh and delicious food. Very good service from waiters
The clean beef in the restaurant is also very delicious.Come here often in the future.

Very good value lunch set hot pot at RM29.90.  With soft drinks and ice cream included . Foods are also up to standard . Though cannot compete with costly Restaruant , but no one can beat its value .

Environment during lunch hours is good . Not crowded , cool and quiet . Highly recommended.
Good service n hygiene as one pot for each person. Set meal instead of buffet style.. Better especially during mco period.
The hotpot here never disappoints! Always pampered with a large quantity of fresh and delicious ingredients, complimented by some drinks and desserts.
